name: node-nats-streaming

scripts.lint: jshint --reporter node_modules/jshint-stylish lib/*.js test/*.js test/support/*.js examples/*.js
scripts.test: npm run depcheck && npm run depcheck:unused && npm run lint && npm run test:unit
scripts.test:unit: mkdir -p reports/ && NODE_ENV=test multi='spec=- xunit=reports/mocha-xunit.xml' istanbul cover _mocha -- -R mocha-multi --exit --timeout 10000 --slow 750 && istanbul check-coverage
